---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Technik Logistyk - ZSEiU Łaziska Górne" description="Technik logistyk w ZSEiU Łaziska Górne – zarządzanie transportem, organizacja magazynów (SPL.01, SPL.04), systemy WMS/ERP, współpraca z bekuplast S.A. i Erasmus+.">

  <article class="w-full max-w-5xl mx-auto min-w-0">

    <!-- HERO -->
    <div class="relative overflow-hidden rounded-2xl bg-linear-to-br from-slate-900 via-blue-950 to-slate-900 dark:from-navy-950 dark:via-blue-950/70 dark:to-navy-950 border border-slate-700/50 dark:border-blue-900/30 p-5 sm:p-10 mb-10 w-full">
      <div class="logistics-grid absolute inset-0 opacity-20" aria-hidden="true"></div>
      <div class="logistics-glow absolute -top-20 -right-20 w-80 h-80 bg-blue-500/10 rounded-full blur-3xl pointer-events-none" aria-hidden="true"></div>
      <div class="logistics-glow absolute -bottom-20 -left-20 w-80 h-80 bg-cyan-500/10 rounded-full blur-3xl pointer-events-none" aria-hidden="true"></div>
      <div class="relative z-10">
        <span class="inline-block px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-semibold bg-blue-500/20 text-blue-300 border border-blue-500/30 mb-4">Technikum w ZSEiU</span>
        <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-5xl font-extrabold text-white mb-3 leading-tight wrap-break-word">Technik <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-linear-to-r from-blue-300 via-sky-400 to-cyan-400">Logistyk</span></h1>
        <p class="text-base sm:text-xl text-slate-300 max-w-2xl leading-relaxed wrap-break-word">Zarządzaj przepływem świata – planowanie dostaw, nowoczesne magazyny, transport i spedycja międzynarodowa.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- STATYSTYKI -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-2 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-3 sm:gap-4 my-10 w-full">
      <div class="stat-card rounded-xl bg-white dark:bg-navy-800/70 border border-slate-200 dark:border-navy-700 p-3 sm:p-5 text-center min-w-0" data-count-to="5">
        <span class="block text-2xl sm:text-4xl font-extrabold text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400"><span class="stat-value">0</span> lat</span>
        <span class="block mt-1 text-xs sm:text-base text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 leading-snug">nauki w technikum</span>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-card rounded-xl bg-white dark:bg-navy-800/70 border border-slate-200 dark:border-navy-700 p-3 sm:p-5 text-center min-w-0" data-count-to="2">
        <span class="block text-2xl sm:text-4xl font-extrabold text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400"><span class="stat-value">0</span></span>
        <span class="block mt-1 text-xs sm:text-base text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 leading-snug">kwalifikacje zawodowe (SPL.01, SPL.04)</span>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-card rounded-xl bg-white dark:bg-navy-800/70 border border-slate-200 dark:border-navy-700 p-3 sm:p-5 text-center min-w-0" data-count-to="100">
        <span class="block text-2xl sm:text-4xl font-extrabold text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400"><span class="stat-value">0</span>%</span>
        <span class="block mt-1 text-xs sm:text-base text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 leading-snug">pewności zatrudnienia w branży TSL</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- TECHNOLOGIE -->
    <h2 class="text-xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mt-10 mb-6 pl-3 sm:pl-4 border-l-4 border-blue-500 leading-snug wrap-break-word">Obszary i technologie w logistyce</h2>

    <p class="text-base sm:text-lg leading-relaxed text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300 mb-6 wrap-break-word">
      Współczesna logistyka opiera się na zaawansowanych systemach bazodanowych, automatycznej identyfikacji i zintegrowanym zarządzaniu.
    </p>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-2 xs:grid-cols-3 sm:grid-cols-4 lg:grid-cols-7 gap-3 mb-8 w-full">
      <div class="tech-chip rounded-xl bg-white dark:bg-navy-800/70 border border-slate-200 dark:border-navy-700 p-3 sm:p-4 text-center min-w-0 hover:border-blue-400 dark:hover:border-blue-600 hover:shadow-md transition-all duration-300">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 mx-auto mb-2 rounded-lg bg-slate-100 dark:bg-navy-700 flex items-center justify-center text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300 shrink-0">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" class="w-6 h-6"><rect x="3" y="3" width="18" height="18" rx="2"></rect><path d="M9 3v18M15 3v18M3 9h18M3 15h18"></path></svg>
        </div>
        <span class="block text-xs sm:text-sm font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-white wrap-break-word">Magazyny WMS</span>
      </div>
      <div class="tech-chip rounded-xl bg-white dark:bg-navy-800/70 border border-slate-200 dark:border-navy-700 p-3 sm:p-4 text-center min-w-0 hover:border-blue-400 dark:hover:border-blue-600 hover:shadow-md transition-all duration-300">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 mx-auto mb-2 rounded-lg bg-slate-100 dark:bg-navy-700 flex items-center justify-center text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300 shrink-0">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" class="w-6 h-6"><ellipse cx="12" cy="5" rx="9" ry="3"></ellipse><path d="M21 12c0 1.66-4 3-9 3s-9-1.34-9-3"></path><path d="M3 5v14c0 1.66 4 3 9 3s9-1.34 9-3V5"></path></svg>
        </div>
        <span class="block text-xs sm:text-sm font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-white wrap-break-word">Systemy ERP</span>
      </div>
      <div class="tech-chip rounded-xl bg-white dark:bg-navy-800/70 border border-slate-200 dark:border-navy-700 p-3 sm:p-4 text-center min-w-0 hover:border-blue-400 dark:hover:border-blue-600 hover:shadow-md transition-all duration-300">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 mx-auto mb-2 rounded-lg bg-slate-100 dark:bg-navy-700 flex items-center justify-center text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300 shrink-0">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" class="w-6 h-6"><rect x="1" y="3" width="15" height="13" rx="2"></rect><path d="M16 8h4l3 5v3h-7V8z"></path><circle cx="5.5" cy="18.5" r="2.5"></circle><circle cx="18.5" cy="18.5" r="2.5"></circle></svg>
        </div>
        <span class="block text-xs sm:text-sm font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-white wrap-break-word">Spedycja</span>
      </div>
      <div class="tech-chip rounded-xl bg-white dark:bg-navy-800/70 border border-slate-200 dark:border-navy-700 p-3 sm:p-4 text-center min-w-0 hover:border-blue-400 dark:hover:border-blue-600 hover:shadow-md transition-all duration-300">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 mx-auto mb-2 rounded-lg bg-slate-100 dark:bg-navy-700 flex items-center justify-center text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300 shrink-0">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" class="w-6 h-6"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle><path d="M12 2a14.5 14.5 0 0 0 0 20 14.5 14.5 0 0 0 0-20M2 12h20"></path></svg>
        </div>
        <span class="block text-xs sm:text-sm font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-white wrap-break-word">Incoterms</span>
      </div>
      <div class="tech-chip rounded-xl bg-white dark:bg-navy-800/70 border border-slate-200 dark:border-navy-700 p-3 sm:p-4 text-center min-w-0 hover:border-blue-400 dark:hover:border-blue-600 hover:shadow-md transition-all duration-300">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 mx-auto mb-2 rounded-lg bg-slate-100 dark:bg-navy-700 flex items-center justify-center text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300 shrink-0">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" class="w-6 h-6"><path d="M20 7l-8 4-8-4"></path><path d="M12 21V11"></path><path d="M4 7v10l8 4 8-4V7"></path></svg>
        </div>
        <span class="block text-xs sm:text-sm font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-white wrap-break-word">E-commerce</span>
      </div>
      <div class="tech-chip rounded-xl bg-white dark:bg-navy-800/70 border border-slate-200 dark:border-navy-700 p-3 sm:p-4 text-center min-w-0 hover:border-blue-400 dark:hover:border-blue-600 hover:shadow-md transition-all duration-300">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 mx-auto mb-2 rounded-lg bg-slate-100 dark:bg-navy-700 flex items-center justify-center text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300 shrink-0">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" class="w-6 h-6"><path d="M3 18h18M3 6h18M3 12h18"></path></svg>
        </div>
        <span class="block text-xs sm:text-sm font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-white wrap-break-word">Kody kreskowe</span>
      </div>
      <div class="tech-chip rounded-xl bg-white dark:bg-navy-800/70 border border-slate-200 dark:border-navy-700 p-3 sm:p-4 text-center min-w-0 hover:border-blue-400 dark:hover:border-blue-600 hover:shadow-md transition-all duration-300">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 mx-auto mb-2 rounded-lg bg-slate-100 dark:bg-navy-700 flex items-center justify-center text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300 shrink-0">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" class="w-6 h-6"><rect x="3" y="11" width="18" height="10" rx="2"></rect><path d="M12 2v9M7 5l5-3 5 3"></path></svg>
        </div>
        <span class="block text-xs sm:text-sm font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-white wrap-break-word">RFID & Barcodes</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- CZEGO SIĘ NAUCZYSZ -->
    <h2 class="text-xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mt-10 mb-6 pl-3 sm:pl-4 border-l-4 border-blue-500 leading-snug wrap-break-word">Czego nauczysz się podczas nauki?</h2>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4 mb-8 w-full">
      <div class="skill-card rounded-xl bg-white dark:bg-navy-800/70 border border-slate-200 dark:border-navy-700 p-4 sm:p-5 hover:shadow-md hover:border-blue-400 dark:hover:border-blue-600 transition-all duration-300 min-w-0">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <span class="shrink-0 w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-blue-100 dark:bg-blue-900/40 flex items-center justify-center text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="w-5 h-5"><rect x="3" y="3" width="18" height="18" rx="2"></rect><path d="M9 3v18M15 3v18M3 9h18M3 15h18"></path></svg>
          </span>
          <div class="min-w-0 flex-1">
            <h3 class="font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white wrap-break-word">Obsługa i organizacja magazynów</h3>
            <ul class="mt-2 space-y-1 text-sm text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 list-disc list-inside">
              <li>przyjmowanie, przechowywanie i wydawanie towarów</li>
              <li>prowadzenie dokumentacji magazynowej (systemy ERP / WMS)</li>
              <li>kontrola stanów magazynowych i inwentaryzacja</li>
              <li>projektowanie optymalnego rozmieszczenia towarów</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="skill-card rounded-xl bg-white dark:bg-navy-800/70 border border-slate-200 dark:border-navy-700 p-4 sm:p-5 hover:shadow-md hover:border-blue-400 dark:hover:border-blue-600 transition-all duration-300 min-w-0">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <span class="shrink-0 w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-blue-100 dark:bg-blue-900/40 flex items-center justify-center text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="w-5 h-5"><rect x="1" y="3" width="15" height="13" rx="2"></rect><path d="M16 8h4l3 5v3h-7V8z"></path><circle cx="5.5" cy="18.5" r="2.5"></circle><circle cx="18.5" cy="18.5" r="2.5"></circle></svg>
          </span>
          <div class="min-w-0 flex-1">
            <h3 class="font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white wrap-break-word">Planowanie transportu i spedycja</h3>
            <ul class="mt-2 space-y-1 text-sm text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 list-disc list-inside">
              <li>dobór optymalnych środków transportu (drogowy, kolejowy, lotniczy, morski)</li>
              <li>planowanie tras i harmonogramów dostaw w systemach GIS</li>
              <li>opracowywanie dokumentacji spedycyjnej krajowej i międzynarodowej</li>
              <li>rozliczanie kosztów transportu</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="skill-card rounded-xl bg-white dark:bg-navy-800/70 border border-slate-200 dark:border-navy-700 p-4 sm:p-5 hover:shadow-md hover:border-blue-400 dark:hover:border-blue-600 transition-all duration-300 min-w-0">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <span class="shrink-0 w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-blue-100 dark:bg-blue-900/40 flex items-center justify-center text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="w-5 h-5"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"></path></svg>
          </span>
          <div class="min-w-0 flex-1">
            <h3 class="font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white wrap-break-word">Logistyka zaopatrzenia i produkcji</h3>
            <ul class="mt-2 space-y-1 text-sm text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 list-disc list-inside">
              <li>zarządzanie zapasami i planowanie zapotrzebowania na materiały</li>
              <li>optymalizacja łańcucha dostaw w przedsiębiorstwie</li>
              <li>współpraca z dostawcami i koordynacja przepływu surowców</li>
              <li>zasada Lean Management i technika Just in Time</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="skill-card rounded-xl bg-white dark:bg-navy-800/70 border border-slate-200 dark:border-navy-700 p-4 sm:p-5 hover:shadow-md hover:border-blue-400 dark:hover:border-blue-600 transition-all duration-300 min-w-0">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <span class="shrink-0 w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-blue-100 dark:bg-blue-900/40 flex items-center justify-center text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="w-5 h-5"><path d="M22 12h-4l-3 9L9 3l-3 9H2"></path></svg>
          </span>
          <div class="min-w-0 flex-1">
            <h3 class="font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white wrap-break-word">Systemy IT w logistyce</h3>
            <ul class="mt-2 space-y-1 text-sm text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 list-disc list-inside">
              <li>obsługa zintegrowanych systemów klasy ERP (np. SAP, Comarch)</li>
              <li>praca w systemach WMS i TMS</li>
              <li>wykorzystanie arkuszy kalkulacyjnych w analizach logistycznych</li>
              <li>konfigurowanie automatycznej identyfikacji (kody kreskowe, RFID)</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="skill-card rounded-xl bg-white dark:bg-navy-800/70 border border-slate-200 dark:border-navy-700 p-4 sm:p-5 hover:shadow-md hover:border-blue-400 dark:hover:border-blue-600 transition-all duration-300 min-w-0">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <span class="shrink-0 w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-blue-100 dark:bg-blue-900/40 flex items-center justify-center text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="w-5 h-5"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle><path d="M12 2a14.5 14.5 0 0 0 0 20 14.5 14.5 0 0 0 0-20M2 12h20"></path></svg>
          </span>
          <div class="min-w-0 flex-1">
            <h3 class="font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white wrap-break-word">Logistyka międzynarodowa i procedury celne</h3>
            <ul class="mt-2 space-y-1 text-sm text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 list-disc list-inside">
              <li>znajomość reguł handlowych Incoterms</li>
              <li>obsługa dokumentów celnych i przewozowych w transporcie transgranicznym</li>
              <li>organizacja spedycji morskiej i lotniczej</li>
              <li>zarządzanie logistyką w e-commerce międzynarodowym</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="skill-card rounded-xl bg-white dark:bg-navy-800/70 border border-slate-200 dark:border-navy-700 p-4 sm:p-5 hover:shadow-md hover:border-blue-400 dark:hover:border-blue-600 transition-all duration-300 min-w-0">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <span class="shrink-0 w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-blue-100 dark:bg-blue-900/40 flex items-center justify-center text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="w-5 h-5"><path d="M17 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H5a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"></path><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"></circle><path d="M23 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87"></path><path d="M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75"></path></svg>
          </span>
          <div class="min-w-0 flex-1">
            <h3 class="font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white wrap-break-word">Zarządzanie i negocjacje</h3>
            <ul class="mt-2 space-y-1 text-sm text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 list-disc list-inside">
              <li>prowadzenie negocjacji z przewoźnikami i dostawcami</li>
              <li>zarządzanie relacjami z klientem (CRM)</li>
              <li>zarządzanie zespołem pracowników magazynowych</li>
              <li>rachunkowość i planowanie budżetu logistycznego</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- TIMELINE 5 LAT -->
    <h2 class="text-xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mt-10 mb-6 pl-3 sm:pl-4 border-l-4 border-blue-500 leading-snug wrap-break-word">Jak wygląda nauka przez 5 lat?</h2>

    <p class="text-base sm:text-lg leading-relaxed text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300 mb-6 wrap-break-word">
      Kształcenie trwa 5 lat i łączy przedmioty ogólne, zawodowe oraz praktyczną naukę w firmach partnerskich.
    </p>

    <div class="relative mb-8 w-full">
      <div class="hidden sm:block absolute left-1/2 top-0 bottom-0 w-0.5 bg-slate-200 dark:bg-navy-700 -translate-x-1/2"></div>
      <div class="space-y-6">
        <div class="relative flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-start gap-4 sm:gap-8">
          <div class="hidden sm:flex sm:w-1/2 justify-end">
            <div class="text-right">
              <span class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-slate-200 dark:bg-navy-700 text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 font-bold text-sm mb-1">I</span>
              <h3 class="font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white">Podstawy logistyki i magazynowania</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400">Pojęcia logistyczne, typy magazynów, podstawy BHP</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="hidden sm:flex shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-blue-500 items-center justify-center ring-4 ring-white dark:ring-navy-900 z-10">
            <span class="text-white font-bold text-xs">1</span>
          </div>
          <div class="w-full sm:w-1/2">
            <div class="sm:hidden flex items-center gap-3 mb-1">
              <span class="shrink-0 w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-blue-500 flex items-center justify-center ring-2 ring-white dark:ring-navy-900"><span class="text-white font-bold text-xs">1</span></span>
              <h3 class="font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white min-w-0 flex-1 wrap-break-word">Klasa I – Podstawy logistyki</h3>
            </div>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 sm:hidden">Pojęcia logistyczne, typy magazynów, podstawy BHP</p>
            <p class="hidden sm:block text-sm text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 mt-1">Uczysz się podstawowych procesów logistycznych, poznajesz rodzaje budowli magazynowych oraz narzędzia do składowania.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="relative flex flex-col sm:flex-row-reverse items-start gap-4 sm:gap-8">
          <div class="hidden sm:flex sm:w-1/2">
            <div>
              <span class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-slate-200 dark:bg-navy-700 text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 font-bold text-sm mb-1">II</span>
              <h3 class="font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white">Procesy magazynowe i systemy IT</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400">Dokumentacja magazynowa, kody kreskowe, systemy WMS</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="hidden sm:flex shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-blue-500 items-center justify-center ring-4 ring-white dark:ring-navy-900 z-10">
            <span class="text-white font-bold text-xs">2</span>
          </div>
          <div class="w-full sm:w-1/2 sm:text-right">
            <div class="sm:hidden flex items-center gap-3 mb-1">
              <span class="shrink-0 w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-blue-500 flex items-center justify-center ring-2 ring-white dark:ring-navy-900"><span class="text-white font-bold text-xs">2</span></span>
              <h3 class="font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white min-w-0 flex-1 wrap-break-word">Klasa II – Magazyny i systemy IT</h3>
            </div>
